DRDGold Sees Gold Production Rising About 10% to 265,000 Ounces Next Year

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-15T10:10:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/drdgold-sees-gold-production-rising-about-10-to-265-000-ounces-next-year.html
DRDGold Ltd. (DRD)  said it expects gold
production for the 12 months to June 2011 to be about 10 percent
higher at about 265,000 ounces compared with a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  